      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail has been preserved to an exacting degree. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
