    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and it\u2019s in truly pristine, flawless condition. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found! It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I\u2019m really going to miss it, but I\u2019m excited for it to find a great new home. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
