    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, quite simply, the finest example of this model you will find on the market today. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather bolsters show no signs of creasing, and the interior still retains that distinct new-car aroma. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function with surgical precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented by a comprehensive binder of service records. It drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a vehicle that just rolled off the assembly line. This is a true collector-grade gem for the buyer who demands absolute perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
