      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been meticulously maintained to meet the highest standards of excellence. Boasting a comprehensive service history and uncompromising mechanical integrity, this offering provides a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a truly distinguished asset in peerless condition.",
