      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the lot\u2014totally pristine and drives like an absolute dream! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, you won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It\u2019s the perfect ride if you're looking for that brand-new feel without the dealership headache. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
