      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, presenting in showroom-original condition. This A80 chassis retains its factory-spec 2JZ-GTE inline-six engine, featuring the original sequential twin-turbocharger arrangement and unmodified induction system. Power is delivered through the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque distribution. The double-wishbone suspension geometry remains tight and responsive, with all bushings and dampers showing no signs of fatigue. The exterior retains its factory paint with matching VIN tags on all panels, while the undercarriage is exceptionally clean, free of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a rare, unmodified example of over-engineered Japanese performance, maintained to the highest mechanical standards.",
